d":false,"created_time":1545841368,"updated_time":1545841368,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你跟我好像啊 。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以我不看好你……希望你被打击后不要灰心，不要管他们的冷嘲热讽，继续追逐自己喜欢的事情。如果出现了那万分之一的可能……我恨不得把脸伸过来给你打\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561381347,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ff767f127b0cffc93784624e35dfb42c","url_token":"mao-hua-91-58","name":"猫华","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ff767f127b0cffc93784624e35dfb42c","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561381347","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545963598,"updated_time":1545963598,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"这个大概也是我在高中所面临的问题吧，不自量，根本不清楚自己有多大本事，看了点名人传记，读了点科普作品，就觉得这天容不下自己了，总想干一番大事出来，最小也要震惊世人吧，殊不知连独立生活都不一定做的到。\u003cbr\u003e你觉得自己了解一大堆浅显的知识就可以触类旁通，解决一大堆世界性难题了，这是不可能的，你先拿本高数，随便翻开一页都会了，再去回到这个问题上。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561235130,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4e2751f31a17807f658da78930dfdd77","url_token":"gao-ge-chui-zi-66","name":"红烧鱼","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-35040ea5b5005a5e07f2c60b9abe35e4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-35040ea5b5005a5e07f2c60b9abe35e4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4e2751f31a17807f658da78930dfdd77","user_type":"people","headline":"从前有个人，很懒","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561235130","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545929917,"updated_time":1545965856,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e只要这个高中生想去就能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e既然问题开脑洞了，那就接着脑洞畅想下去…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先，一个天才高中生在某期刊或者会议发表证明了“哥”的过程并被认可，然后全世界各大主流媒体轰炸式报道。第一批找上该天才的是记者，但是短暂的采访很快就会被打断，省市级领导的会面预约会被优先安排。领导向你保证家乡会给其最高的待遇，要求其保证就在地方科研相关机构。正教授是肯定的了，行政级别不太了解，说不定能直接入党，然后提拔到副处(也就是副院长)什么的。当天晚上就会受到国内各大高校终身教授的offer，当然包括清北，短信狂轰滥炸的一晚，包括之间互相爆料的内幕。如果这哥们不是北京人，几天之内就会受到中央领导人接见，提出的条件应该是清北的正教授，会有很好的行政级别，薪酬不一定能高过地方。让你保证一定要留在国内，这次不仅仅是利诱，很有可能伴随着威逼。和中央同一时间来的，还应该有世界各大名校的offer，大部分的国家提出的应该是巨额的薪酬，但像美俄这种强硬派，很有可能会有高级别人物邀约其举家移民，这时的利益很有可能让一个普通人烧坏脑子，然后答应其中一方的请求。看在少年天才的分上，没得到这哥们的势力，无论哪一国都会觉得留他不得。如果选择留在国内会被严格保护，但依然会经常有各种行刺手段。如果一念之差蒙了心答应国外，中国是绝对不会放人的，逮捕软禁是必须的，然后多国向中国施压要求放人，再接下来就是大国博弈了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实这个脑洞最恐怖的地方不仅仅在于“哥”，而在于“高二“，要是个垂暮之人也就不说什么了，一辈子呕心沥血，即便天才至极，大限将至，几乎也就没什么剩余发挥空间了，但是一个十来岁的人，解决了数以百万计的精英束手无策的问题，给他几十年，鬼tm知道这哥们能整出多大一片天。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560153094,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"dfadccf5bd1fe50be3623e21ce922277","url_token":"horace-28-81","name":"Horace","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-14128214065ff749bfbb93cff5242708_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-14128214065ff749bfbb93cff5242708_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/dfadccf5bd1fe50be3623e21ce922277","user_type":"people","headline":"尘世中一个迷途小书童","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560153094","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545813603,"updated_time":1545813603,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e“如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e谁被清华北大数学系保送？被保送到哪？还是被保送到清华北大数学系？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e恕我直言，以您蹩脚的中文表达，证明写出来我们也看不懂。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562708912,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ded48b08e5516cd98f98942b4967ae30","url_token":"czd1230","name":"czd1230","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ded48b08e5516cd98f98942b4967ae30","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562708912","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-123fb2e7a34868084b0436669dcf4729_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546137676,"updated_time":1546153022,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个“高中生”是看过我的新浪博客“崔振东2018”，里面有哥德巴赫猜想和孪生素数猜想的完整证明。欢迎大家查看我的博客。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e博客地址：\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//blog.sina.com.cn/cuizhendong2018\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttp://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003eblog.sina.com.cn/cuizhe\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003endong2018\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class