3e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1020'%20height='1749'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1020\" data-rawheight=\"1749\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5102309cec91273706532fcc748b701b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1020\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6b3804bdf5cb66df468eaa52324565c4_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6b3804bdf5cb66df468eaa52324565c4_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9596e9b24b7f3aba5d22022d4dbfd6c7_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1059\" data-rawheight=\"1759\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3d6847c48ce005ead3ae46128e2dfcb1_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1059\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9596e9b24b7f3aba5d22022d4dbfd6c7_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1059'%20height='1759'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1059\" data-rawheight=\"1759\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3d6847c48ce005ead3ae46128e2dfcb1_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1059\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9596e9b24b7f3aba5d22022d4dbfd6c7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9596e9b24b7f3aba5d22022d4dbfd6c7_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561120745,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1751957936a14f42d20a44376a21386a","url_token":"meng-hui-da-han","name":"梦回大汗","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ffeff4889c4a5309654491887c1d0e5d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ffeff4889c4a5309654491887c1d0e5d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1751957936a14f42d20a44376a21386a","user_type":"people","headline":"评论通知已关闭","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561120745","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545918572,"updated_time":1545918649,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我来总结一下大多数答主的看法：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1.如果能证明出哥德巴赫猜想，那么就算是清北恐怕都容不下题主这尊“大佛”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2.题主无法证明出哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3.很多答主希望题主不要把重点放在证明哥德巴赫猜想上，而是先努力准备高考，到了大学自然有机会深造数学\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e4.“\u003cb\u003e我没别的意思，就是来讽刺你的，虽然我可能连哥猜是什么都不知道，但那无所谓，只要把不切实际的想法抨击一通就完事了\u003c/b\u003e”（极少数答主）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望题主可以把第三条内容认真考虑一下。我高中虽然是文科生，但是也很喜欢数学，高中时文科数学的各种练习册也做了不少。但代价自然就是偏科，而且高考的时候数学还发挥失常了。不过幸运的是语文和英语居然超常发挥，把总分拉到了正常水平，要不然我的高考就算是失败了。个人认为作为一名偏科的高中生，还是先把偏科的部分补足更加重要。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e自信是好事，但盲目的自信是不好的。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eps：那位匿名的老师真的是很暖了。明年再战教师资格证，希望以后我可以成为像他（她）一样的老师吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561119924,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3e5eae963c49d3e5c3b52f1538ad6a84","url_token":"tian-xia-wu-shuang-38-8","name":"天下无双","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a2cc66b02cfe17d4b871c8069e34d32_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a2cc66b02cfe17d4b871c8069e34d32_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3e5eae963c49d3e5c3b52f1538ad6a84","user_type":"people","headline":"业余读书人","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561119924","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545918485,"updated_time":1545918485,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e    可能像我一样不想泼冷水的.没几个了呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e   我向来敬佩那些敢于在数学道路上不懈前行、勇攀高峰之人，更是对真诚的提出自己的看法，不在乎失败之后遭遇他人的讥讽与藐视的勇者分外珍惜。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e   哥德巴赫猜想是数学王冠的最璀璨的明珠，确实对于一名高中生来说，在该领域，肤浅且浮于表面的认知会极大的限制他的证明与思考。但能够提出自己的看法，同时不是“沽名钓誉”，我大概是不会赞同他的做法，但我会尊敬他的选择。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    民科泛滥，多少“大师”自称解决各式难题，领域非常广泛，已经让大家们忍无可忍。前不久黎曼猜想被热烈讨论后，果不其然“涌现”出一大批“砖家學者”发表看法，自然也接收到了大家们“真诚的祝福”。他们多是认准自己的看法，坚持自己的看法，用不严密的证明与并不合理的推理逻辑，做出一个又一个伪证，自然为大家所不屑。然而对一名确确实实有一定想法、热爱数学的高中生，过分的苛责与嘲讽，或许并不必要。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    1月1日，结果似乎已经十分明了，但我依然会尊重他，尊重他的行为。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    说句实话 问题下面的许多答主，数学能力能不能达到题主的实力...还是另说，先来讥讽一顿算啥事。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560591706,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"62d830169a380e327d90871da9d1fff5","url_token":"quark-37","name":"Quark","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dd37a5850e6ce1dba12d34901f6a27d6_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dd37a5850e6ce1dba12d34901f6a27d6_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/62d830169a380e327d90871da9d1fff5","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560591706","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545872218,"updated_time":1545888747,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我现在大一\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以前看了哥德巴赫猜想这看似简单的题干后也想着自己能不能证明呢\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是最后我还是没有去做这样的梦\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或许题主是个数学天才马上将会横空出世，这当然好，别说保送清北，你已经可以冠上国际知名数学家的称号了，名字会被载入史册。到时候北大清华跪舔你都来不及\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，假如你发表出来被指出错了被冷嘲热讽，你也不要太难受，作为一个高中生你已经很有勇气了。虚心接受错误，好好学习完善自己\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看到那么多答案的冷嘲热讽，希望给点宽容吧，毕竟题主才高中........\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559720137,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c345027c990a2d18451df983bac7c5c4","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559720137","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545754831,"updated_time":1545754831,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e会。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e类似地有，“如果太阳从西边出来，那么天空会下银币雨。”这在逻辑学上是一个真命题。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562424613,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"89e659a946bb05a3202d920d90e88372","url_token":"mei-yitian-huan-le","name":"每一天欢乐","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c8f159c4c2909499be1958c9f4ac737c_is.jpg","avat